data.description: Seller says it's time! $49,000 discount from the original listing price! WOW! Don't miss out! Submit your offers now and own this home with potential EQUITY right away! A deal like this doesn't come by often during a hot market. Hurry! It won't last at this new low price! Call NOW! Uncover the hidden gem within this home, just waiting for your personal touch! 3 Bedroom and 2 Bathroom. U-shaped Kitchen layout optimizes workflow for cooking and meal preparation. Laundry room with a great quantity of cabinets. Outdoor drying stand right outside the laundry room. Attached garage can store up to 2 cars. Pull down the attic stairs in garage and find yourself with sufficient attic space for a ''man cave''. Possible RV access to the right side of home. Generous lot size offers endless landscaping possibilities. Desirable neighborhood with rising property values - an excellent long-term investment. Consider the Mojave Inland Port project. Schedule a viewing today before someone else does and unlock the potential of this fantastic property and the opportunity to have INSTANT EQUITY!
